TopPrio:

* networkmanager / applet:
	* AP default configuration for fixed IP:
		1. Setup fixed IP for wlan0 (should be in same net as range below)
		2. Setup dnsmasq.conf
			domain-needed
			bogus-priv
			bind-dynamic
			listen-address=<fixed IP above>  OR interface wlan0
			dhcp-range=interface:wlan0,<start-IP>,<end-IP>
		3. systemctl restart dnsmasq
	* AP default configuration for fixed IP:
		1. Setup shared for wlan0 (TBD)

* kernel:
